title: Jenna Elfman
itunes:title: Jenna Elfman
description:
Jenna Elfman [Fear the Walking Dead, Dharma & Greg, Keeping the Faith, EDtv] and Anna discuss podcasting, making marriage work, sitcoms, zombies, driving fast, and more.


Today’s Unqualified segment begins with a call from Patrick, who has been in a loving relationship for two years but wishes that his partner’s family knew that he was more than a roommate. 


Anna and Jenna then talk with Margaret who was diagnosed with bipolar disorder, ADHD and autism, all in the span of a year. After taking some time to reflect, Margaret wonders how this new understanding about herself relates to her family, friends, and potential partners.


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
